data.description: This 1-story with finished basement brims with untapped potential! New exterior siding and paint in 2020, complement a charming interior with gleaming wood floors and plush carpeting. The main-level features a private primary suite and the remodeled utility room adds modern convenience. In the basement you will find 2 bedrooms, a flex room, a full bathroom and a finished room with closet, which can be used as a 4th bedroom. 2.6 acres of private, tree-lined property awaits, capturing the essence of Pacific Northwest living. Fully-fenced areas cater to pets/livestock, and a soothing hot tub beckons. Situated just 5.5 miles from the Island Ferry, you're effortlessly connected to the city of Seattle. Island living has never been more inviting!
